author: Katie Richcreek
title: Tony Romo Tells Tom Brady 'See You in February' After Cowboys-Patriots Game
text:
Tony Romo Tells Tom Brady 'See You in February' After Cowboys-Patriots Game Bleacher Report 15 hrs ago Katie Richcreek Â© Vine Tony Romo might have been sidelined for Sunday's 30-6 loss to the New England Patriots, but the injured Dallas Cowboys quarterback is still quite confident.
AdChoices It would at least appear that way.
When Romo approached Tom Brady after the game, he casually dropped these four small words: "See you in February."
